<br>
Things we going good...rocking along, slaying our way nicely thru stack after stack of Dolvargs, curates, callers etc...<br>
<br>
Then I look up and the cleric health is spirally down in a hurry.  The puller was deep into KC doing his job we were all practically against the wall waiting our turn to kill....talking in GC, in tells and in group chat.  I had enough time to turn and taunt and mash the attack buttun before the cleric was dead to a spectral caller....where the heck did he come from??<br>
<br>
Cleric said he popped right on him.  I have hunted in KC a lot....not on this server but on the old one.  I know at times if you mess up a pull they sometimes pop on you at the front but usually that is after you have actually ran to the front as a puller.  This one just materialized outa no where.<br>
<br>
/shakes fist at VI.<br>
<br>
